Day 3 – AI Lead Qualification Agent
Objective

Build an AI-powered Lead Qualification Agent using n8n and OpenAI. The goal is to automate the first step of the sales process by analyzing inbound leads and generating structured outputs that can be consumed by CRM systems and downstream automations.

Problem

Sales teams spend significant time manually reviewing inbound leads to determine:

Whether the lead is qualified
How quickly they should be contacted
Which representative should own the lead
What personalized outreach should be sent

This manual process is inconsistent, slow, and difficult to scale.

Solution

Developed an AI-powered workflow that accepts lead information, analyzes it using OpenAI, and returns structured JSON containing qualification data.

