Key Learnings
AI responses should always be structured for downstream systems.
Standardized JSON enables reliable automation.
Prompt engineering significantly impacts output quality.
Business rules should be explicit rather than inferred by the model.
AI is most valuable when embedded into operational workflows.
Portfolio Value

This project demonstrates how AI can automate lead qualification, prioritize inbound opportunities, and reduce manual effort for Sales and Revenue Operations teams. It serves as the foundation for a larger GTM automation platform that will integrate CRM, enrichment tools, messaging platforms, and analytics.
